  "prompt": "How much is hootsuite?",
  "response": "Hootsuite offers several pricing plans tailored to different needs, ranging from individuals and small teams to large businesses and enterprises. As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, here are the typical pricing tiers:\n\n1. **Free Plan**\n   - **Cost:** $0/month\n   - **Features:**\n     - Manage up to 2 social media accounts\n     - Basic message scheduling\n     - Limited access to analytics\n\n2. **Professional Plan**\n   - **Cost:** Approximately $49 per month (billed annually)\n   - **Features:**\n     - Manage up to 10 social media accounts\n     - Unlimited scheduling\n     - Access to premium apps and integrations\n     - Basic analytics\n\n3. **Team Plan**\n   - **Cost:** Approximately $129 per month (billed annually)\n   - **Features:**\n     - Manage up to 20 social media accounts\n     - Collaborate with team members\n     - Enhanced analytics and reporting\n     - Content approvals\n\n4. **Business Plan**\n   - **Cost:** Approximately $739 per month (billed annually)\n   - **Features:**\n     - Manage up to 35 social media accounts\n     - Advanced analytics and custom reporting\n     - Enhanced security features\n     - Dedicated support\n\n5. **Enterprise Plan**\n   - **Cost:** Custom pricing based on specific needs\n   - **Features:**\n     - Tailored solutions for large organizations\n     - Advanced integrations and API access\n     - Dedicated account management\n     - Comprehensive support and training\n\n**Please Note:**\n- Pricing may vary based on promotions, region, or updates made by Hootsuite after October 2023.\n- Annual billing often comes with discounts compared to monthly billing.\n- Hootsuite occasionally offers additional features or adjustments to their plans, so it's a good idea to review the current offerings directly on their [official pricing page](https://www.hootsuite.com/plans).\n\nIf you have specific requirements or need more detailed information, visiting the Hootsuite website or contacting their sales team would provide the most accurate and up-to-date information.",
